/activity_matrix/*  https://soma-853c.onrender.com/activity_matrix/:splat  200

# --- CSS, backend static → proxy a Render (rutas especiales fuera del repo root) ---
/css/*  https://soma-853c.onrender.com/css/:splat  200
/backend/*  https://soma-853c.onrender.com/backend/:splat  200

